readme:
# bitcoder-syntax theme

A theme which divides codes in.. little colored **bits**. Aims to readability, cleanness and atomic brackets/tags highlighting.

This is my first theme for Atom and my first Github repository. :smiley:
Feel free to give me advices, if needed.

*(It is a fork of Genesis, though no more recognizable)*

![A screenshot of your theme](https://github.com/bitkris-dev/bitcoder-syntax/blob/master/bitcoder1.png?raw=true)
